70010000075176.description:
Take control of a wide range of boats and speedboats, each with their own unique handling characteristics. Your goal is to moor your ship at the specified point, avoiding collisions with various obstacles.

Test your skills in a variety of levels, each presenting a unique set of challenges. Maneuver through narrow channels, avoid static buildings and dodge moving boats to safely dock your ship.

As you progress through the game, the difficulty will increase, requiring more and more precision and skill from you. Experience the thrill of boat control like never before and become a water parking master. Get ready for an exciting adventure that will test your skills and provide hours of addictive gameplay!

GAME FEATURES:
• Excellent warm-up for attentiveness and accuracy;
• Many levels with varying difficulty;
• Exciting gameplay for all ages;
• Realistic graphics and boat control physics;

70010000075240.description:
You will become a real interior designer specializing in kitchens. Your creative vision and problem-solving skills will be put to the test as you will need to arrange furniture and other items in the limited kitchen space, creating a cozy and functional environment.

The game provides a wide selection of kitchen furniture. You can experiment with different styles and create unique designs. And with a variety of tableware, from elegant porcelain sets to colorful ceramic bowls, you can add some flair to your project.

But remember that space is limited! You'll need to be smart to make the most of every inch of your kitchen. Arrange furniture to provide ample room for movement and create a comfortable work area. Every decision you make will impact the overall functionality and aesthetics of your kitchen.

The game offers creative freedom and the satisfaction of creating a beautiful and functional space. So let your design imagination run wild and you can turn ordinary kitchens into stunning masterpieces!

GAME FEATURES:
• An excellent warm-up for attentiveness and ingenuity;
• Many different types of furniture and cutlery;
• Exciting gameplay for all ages;

70010000048756.description:
Prepare for cuteness overload, relentless training, and fierce rivalry as you and your hamsters take on challenges while traversing the maze, riding a skateboard, and more! Be the first to cross the finish line to earn rewards and yummy treats!

FEATURES:
- Experience fierce competition in a laid-back style – all you need is a single button, but don't think for one second that it means you won’t break a sweat!
- Race and compete with AI-driven hamsters or other players in multiplayer modes – compete with others, whether they're next to you, or hundreds of miles away;
- Develop your hamsters’ abilities and skillsets to compete against higher-level opponents;
- Look after your hamsters and expand their house – furnish it with new equipment and make it the mansion they deserve;
- Name your hamsters and customize them – there are over 100 cosmetic items!
- Enjoy detailed graphics and cute animations, no matter what mode you're playing!

70050000046138.description:
Spooky Hamster House DLC is the expansion pack for Hamster Playground – a fresh dash of content to enrich your experience! Our hamsters are keen on celebrating social events and they are more than ready to dip their paws into the foggy waters of unknown and scary.
Help them by redecorating their house in a spooky way and dressing them up in new costumes that would not be out of place at a zombie prom! Complete fresh quests and experience a new, deliciously witchy hamster job.

Spooky Hamster House DLC features:
new, spooky items for the hamster house;
new, scary costumes;
brand-new quests with unique rewards;
a super spooky job for your hamsters!
